---
// Get Personalized Comparison CTA Component
---

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-4">
      Why Get a Personalized Comparison?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-red-100 text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      We don't just show you rates – we provide insider expertise that helps you make the right choice for YOUR situation.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      
      <!-- Benefit 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-white mr-4 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Pre-Existing Conditions Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-red-100 text-sm">We check upfront with Swica (more flexible) before applying. Helsana denies faster – we help you avoid rejections.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-white mr-4 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
            <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Broker-Only Group Discounts</h3>
            <p class="text-red-100 text-sm mb-3">Typically 10-15% less than direct rates. Example with 15% discount:</p>
            <div class="group relative inline-block">
              <button class="text-white underline hover:text-red-200 text-sm">
                See discount examples →
              </button>
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-full mt-2 w-80 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-4 opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all z-10">
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sample Monthly Savings (15% broker discount):</p>
                <div class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-700">
                  <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Swica Optima:</span> <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">CHF 185 → CHF 157</span></div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Helsana Completa:</span> <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">CHF 168 → CHF 143</span></div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Swica Hospital:</span> <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">CHF 320 → CHF 272</span></div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between"><span>Helsana Hospital:</span> <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">CHF 298 → CHF 253</span></div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2 border-t pt-2">Annual savings: CHF 300-600+</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-white mr-4 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Swica's Age-Entry System Explained</h3>
            <p class="text-red-100 text-sm">We explain how Swica locks your supplementary rate at signup age – huge savings if you're under 35. Helsana increases premiums every 5 years.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-white mr-4 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Wellness Benefits Can Cover Your Premiums</h3>
            <p class="text-red-100 text-sm"><strong>Swica</strong> pays up to <strong>CHF 1,300/year</strong> for gym membership. <strong>Helsana</strong> only <strong>CHF 200/year</strong>. This difference alone can offset premium costs!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <button 
        onclick="window.openHealthModal('consultation')"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-red-600 font-bold text-lg rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all"
      >
        Schedule Personalized Comparison
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ml-3 h-6 w-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
          <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <p class="text-red-100 text-sm mt-4">100% free consultation • No obligation • Expert advice in English</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
